Build time paths get to smb.conf.

Default: dns update command =
           /builds/11.4-SRU/11.4.76.0.1.182.1/components/samba/build/amd64/source4/scripting/bin/samba_dnsupdate

smb.conf(5) is installed to prototype directory from source generated during
build time, so get_override() mechanism in dynconfig/wscript will do its job.

Bug 16036 - Build time paths get into smb.conf
https://bugzilla.samba.org/show_bug.cgi?id=16036

--- a/dynconfig/wscript
+++ b/dynconfig/wscript
@@ -401,7 +400,7 @@ def get_override(bld):
                  'LIBEXECDIR'    : 'bin',
                  'SAMBA_LIBEXECDIR' : 'bin',
                  'CODEPAGEDIR'   : 'codepages',
-                 'SCRIPTSBINDIR' : 'source4/scripting/bin',
+                 #'SCRIPTSBINDIR' : 'source4/scripting/bin',
                  'SETUPDIR'      : 'source4/setup'
                  }
     return override
